query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(cn mc) NoMergeJoin(cn mc t) NoMergeJoin(cn mc t ci) NoMergeJoin(ci cn mc t an1) NoHashJoin(an1 ci cn mc t rt) NoHashJoin(an1 ci cn mc rt t n1) */ select min(an1.name) AS costume_designer_pseudo,
min(t.title) AS movie_with_costumes
from company_name AS cn
inner join movie_companies AS mc
on mc.company_id = cn.id AND cn.country_code = '[ru]'
inner join title AS t
on t.id = mc.movie_id
inner join cast_info AS ci
on ci.movie_id = t.id AND ci.movie_id = mc.movie_id
inner join aka_name AS an1
on an1.person_id = ci.person_id
inner join role_type AS rt
on ci.role_id = rt.id AND rt.role = 'producer'
inner join name AS n1
on an1.person_id = n1.id AND n1.id = ci.person_id;
